Package org.jboss.aerogear.android.authentication

Interface Summary
AuthenticationModule A module which can authenticate a user.
AuthType A interface for the types of AuthenticationModule knows how to build.
 

Class Summary
AbstractAuthenticationModule This class stubs out the enroll, login, and logout methods.
AuthenticationConfig This is the minimum (hopefully) necessary parameters for an AuthenticationModule
AuthorizationFields This class wraps up fields which need to be applied to a request to ensure it can be securely consumed.
